{
  "stem": "543.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, I have another friend who has no children, and they want to take you in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, I'll bring you there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The kids know you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The kids knew me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in Haarlem.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in their home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we were in an attic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a room in the-- on the-- on the-- on the-- on the top floor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And those people were fantastic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Enormous good people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The people were-- while we were there, I think my brother-in-law, who was-- who was married to my oldest-- my oldest sister didn't even want to go in hiding before-- she couldn't hide-- hide before me.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She didn't want to go in hiding before all her family was safe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was very, very conscious about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother and my father should be in hiding and everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sophia.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She-- she-- they-- they-- I think they paid some, but very little.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my parents who were still in Amsterdam, the SS came all the time to my parents, and told them, listen, what happened to your daughter and your son-in-law.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See, my mother, who couldn't hear, you know, and said, all the time, I don't know where they are.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they was-- they were very afraid that they would pick them up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were in hiding with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was in-- in hiding place were my father, my mother, my-- my husband, and me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Four, at least four of us in the small attic for year and a half.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't go out of the-- you couldn't go on the street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody's supposed to know that the people were-- and it was very danger to hide people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he was working, and she was cooking for us and doing things for us.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
